{"tid":2285522,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺幸福的彼端係動物台最高質會然","createTime":"2020-11-14T07:24:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T09:09:20.000Z","uid":4618,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"65d7aef3ac596acb7293fc482693fbb6ddbda3c1","tid":2285522,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T07:24:49.000Z","msg":"老實講以前我都覺得覺得佢有少少煩，明明唔關事既topic都入去講刀劍，所以有時會無視佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但日久真係會見人心，連侍奉部假膠都玩厭咗刀劍梗，轉用鬼滅引戰；連戀童狗n腎都屌厭咗烏賊娘，轉去譯幼女h漫...<br />\n<br />\n係得返佢每日不辭勞苦，無論嗰期係興鋼鍊定re0定鬼滅，無論拜登定當撈侵選贏，佢都一定風雨不改地吹奏刀劍同川原礫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個人可以堅持鍾意既事物十年唔係件易事，依家我睇到桐人圖已經唔覺得厭煩，反而有種安心感，因為喺入面係感受到粉絲對作品既愛，呢樣先係真正無價寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會然幸福的彼端，我三日月願稱你為動物台最強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yb478JU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYb478JU.png&h=f4f1021d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3bc815138ede3944a80fa2b20be0f11e30d1880","tid":2285522,"uid":197836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T07:27:41.000Z","msg":"你先係"},{"pid":"5f13bace5d6e36503073287f1b81e06c35a6be02","tid":2285522,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3bc815138ede3944a80fa2b20be0f11e30d1880","tid":2285522,"uid":197836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T07:27:41.000Z","msg":"你先係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T07:29:25.000Z","msg":"我拍馬都追唔上幸福的彼端"},{"pid":"407f26970ad6361f686e2e11fc44c9670e2cb806","tid":2285522,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T07:31:52.000Z","msg":"沙魚450 軟絲850 花蟹750 小的450 再小一點350 大沙母850 海瓜子180 奶油貝250 生蠔180 木瓜螺350 小花籠1250 水姑娘1680 象蚌650"},{"pid":"1fde5fd8d2a8938ab4939912a823d7d36749abf7","tid":2285522,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p